Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Villanueva Central School in the Municipality of Villanueva, Province of Misamis Oriental, to Vicente N. Chaves Memorial Central School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 550
An Act Changing the Name of the Villanueva Central School in the Municipality of Villanueva, Province of Misamis Oriental, to Vicente N. Chaves Memorial Central School
Section 1. The name of the Villanueva Central School in the Municipality of Villanueva, Province of Misamis Oriental, is changed to Vicente N. Chaves Memorial Central School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
